Title: A Remark on Non-conformal Non-supersymmetric Theories with Vanishing

Vacuum Energy DensityAuthors: Olindo Corradini, Alberto Iglesias, Zurab Kakushadze and Peter

LangfelderComments: 13 pages, revtex; a minor change in wording

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A16 (2001) 1761-1773

We discuss non-conformal non-supersymmetric large N gauge theories withvanishing vacuum energy density to all orders in perturbation theory. Thesegauge theories can be obtained via a field theory limit of Type IIB D3-branesembedded in orbifolded space-times. We also discuss gravity in this setup.